</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Opening the settings:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Click on the plentyBase logo in your computer’s task bar and click on <strong>Open configuration</strong>.<br></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
